description:
The 2022 race for Governor of Pennsylvania has proven contentious, if not particularly competitive.  A televised debate between John Fetterman and Dr. Mehmet Oz has been scheduled to take place in Harrisburg, Pennsylvania on October 25, 2022, and is expected to receive widespread national attention. Mr. Fetterman, however, has been reluctant to engage in a debate up to this point, and ongoing complications from a stroke he suffered earlier this year has left people in doubt as to whether the scheduled debate will actually occur.

This market will resolve to "Yes" if the debate between John Fetterman and Dr. Mehmet Oz happens on October 25, 2022. Otherwise, this market will resolve to "No".

This market may not resolve before October 25, 2022.

The primary resolution source will be footage of the debate, however credible reporting may also be used.
